<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>비밀번호 변경</title>
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200"
        />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/base.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/buttons.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/modals.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/edit-password.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <div class="title-header-layout">
            <div class="title-header-container">
                <button class="mobile-nav-toggle">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">menu</span>
                </button>
                <h1 class="title">프로필 관리</h1>
            </div>

            <hr class="divider" />
        </div>
        <main class="main-content">
            <aside class="side-nav">
                <h2 class="side-nav-title">🪄 프로필 관리</h2>
                <hr class="side-nav-divider" />
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/mypage/edit">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"> edit </span>
                            프로필 수정
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/mypage/edit-password" class="active">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                                lock_reset
                            </span>
                            비밀번호 변경
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </aside>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h1 class="card-title">비밀번호 변경</h1>
                    <p class="card-description">
                        보안을 위해 주기적으로 비밀번호를 변경해주세요.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div id="password-form-container"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer" id="password-form-actions"></div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <div class="nav-backdrop"></div>
            <div class="page-layout">
                <aside class="side-nav">
                    <h2 class="side-nav-title">🪄 프로필 관리</h2>
                    <hr class="side-nav-divider" />
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/mypage/edit">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                                    edit
                                </span>
                                프로필 수정
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/mypage/edit-password" class="active">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
                                    lock_reset
                                </span>
                                비밀번호 변경
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </aside>
                <div class="main-panel">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="password-form-body">
                            <div id="current-password-container"></div>
                            <div id="new-password-container"></div>
                            <p class="password-rules">
                                * 비밀번호는 8자 이상, 20자 이하이며, 영문,
                                숫자, 특수문자를 포함해야 합니다.
                            </p>
                            <div id="confirm-password-container"></div>
                            <p
                                class="password-match-status"
                                id="password-match-status"
                            ></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="button-container" id="form-actions">
                            <!-- Buttons are rendered by JS -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <div class="nav-backdrop"></div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

        <div class="notice-container"></div>
        <script src="/edit-password.mjs" type="module"></script>
    </body>
</html>
